Partial Update Plugin Plugin name: partialupdate Description The Partial Update plugin updates elements of an exiting Item from the content of a supplied XML

This plugin provides the ability to add sub elements or update existing elements add sub elements to an existing list of sub-elements starting from a specified position Inputs xml_instance: the XML used to find and update an existing Item.
